INSERT INTO `news_newspage` VALUES (35,1,'Open position: Trainee Industrial Ecology','Open position: Trainee Industrial Ecology',NULL,'Become part of our Science Team','Become part of our Science Team',NULL,'2019-07-29','You love looking at entire systems, dream about material and energy flows, and you can\'t stop talking about numbers and figures. You are the first to note that sustainability can\'t be looked at from an object level only. You want to put your skills to work and change the world around you.   You speak the language of system maps. You would also like to get equipped with  the necessary tools to approach personal growth, complex problems, and translate these into powerful solutions that will be applied in practice. You can reach these goals by joining us at Except Integrated Sustainability.','You love looking at entire systems, dream about material and energy flows, and you can\'t stop talking about numbers and figures. You are the first to note that sustainability can\'t be looked at from an object level only. You want to put your skills to work and change the world around you.   You speak the language of system maps. You would also like to get equipped with  the necessary tools to approach personal growth, complex problems, and translate these into powerful solutions that will be applied in practice. You can reach these goals by joining us at Except Integrated Sustainability.','',NULL,'OP',1,1,'[{\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We\\u2019re working on several projects in urban redevelopment, the food  sector, and industrial transitions. We offer a traineeship for aspiring  industrial ecologists, interested in working on integrated sustainable  solutions from a scientific perspective. You need to be experienced in  data research and, in particular, life cycle assessments.</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"b5ac3284-1acd-49f9-88f7-1e646dd3930f\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>In addition to this, the following is of importance:</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"f4050256-b239-40f4-8b19-4b481ee09078\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<ul><li>You are comfortable working independently, responsibly, but not unsupervised.</li><li>You are creative, a teamplayer, good at coordination, driven, and entrepreneurial.</li><li>You can dream making a life cycle analysis.</li><li>You have experience with system mapping tools (MFA &amp; SFA).</li><li>Your English writing and speaking skills are perfect. Mastering Dutch is a nice bonus.</li><li>You are punctual, precise and professional.</li><li>You like to work on innovative, new approaches.</li><li>You can start today, and are available for the coming 6 months.</li></ul>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"e55f7850-4797-4915-a0f2-3ae3a51a6656\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>Sounds like you? We\\u2019d love to hear from you. Please read our entire <a id=\\\"10\\\" linktype=\\\"page\\\">Work with us page</a> carefully, and follow the procedure stated to apply.</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"36f60f60-ac66-4489-b89f-6c9d5c33ac2e\"}]','[{\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We\\u2019re working on several projects in urban redevelopment, the food  sector, and industrial transitions. We offer a traineeship for aspiring  industrial ecologists, interested in working on integrated sustainable  solutions from a scientific perspective. You need to be experienced in  data research and, in particular, life cycle assessments.</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"b5ac3284-1acd-49f9-88f7-1e646dd3930f\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>In addition to this, the following is of importance:</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"f4050256-b239-40f4-8b19-4b481ee09078\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<ul><li>You are comfortable working independently, responsibly, but not unsupervised.</li><li>You are creative, a teamplayer, good at coordination, driven, and entrepreneurial.</li><li>You can dream making a life cycle analysis.</li><li>You have experience with system mapping tools (MFA &amp; SFA).</li><li>Your English writing and speaking skills are perfect. Mastering Dutch is a nice bonus.</li><li>You are punctual, precise and professional.</li><li>You like to work on innovative, new approaches.</li><li>You can start today, and are available for the coming 6 months.</li></ul>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"e55f7850-4797-4915-a0f2-3ae3a51a6656\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>Sounds like you? We\\u2019d love to hear from you. Please read our entire <a id=\\\"10\\\" linktype=\\\"page\\\">Work with us page</a> carefully, and follow the procedure stated to apply.</p>\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph_block\", \"id\": \"36f60f60-ac66-4489-b89f-6c9d5c33ac2e\"}]','[]',NULL,NULL),(36,1,'X|X Except 20th Anniversary Celebration','X|X Except 20th Anniversary Celebration',NULL,'Join us in celebrating 20 years of integrated sustainability','Join us in celebrating 20 years of integrated sustainability',NULL,'2019-08-12','This year, Except turns 20. For the past two decades, we existed to create the foundations of a sustainable society. As one of the first integrated sustainability organizations in the world, we want to celebrate this milestone with all of you in a truly Except fashion. Please register your attendance, dinner and workshops via this link.','This year, Except turns 20. For the past two decades, we existed to create the foundations of a sustainable society. As one of the first integrated sustainability organizations in the world, we want to celebrate this milestone with all of you in a truly Except fashion. Please register your attendance, dinner and workshops via this link.','',NULL,'EV',1,1,'[{\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We celebrate with the unique and amazing people that have traveled this  path with us together all those years. Expect a full day program, free  workshops, inspiring stories from partners, and a big party at the  end.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"b7d6c806-c653-4ba5-bab8-51effaf4ffd9\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"size\": \"h4\", \"heading_text\": \"Anniversary program\"}, \"id\": \"05f75a66-61ee-4824-b1a2-d03a158fd76a\", \"type\": \"heading_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>During the day, we offer sustainability pioneers multiple free  workshops. What would the world look like in 20 years? Use our SiD  framework to have fun while learning about integrated sustainability.  Eveline Mos will teach you how to envision your own future by using  visual dialogue techniques, and we will share our experiences with  setting up a community garden.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"c2909535-12fe-412a-8804-fb817a6646ad\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We ask our partners to share their stories on their own past and future  journey, and launch the first complete SiD book \\u2013\\u00a0 followed by a dinner  provided by Instock. We end with a party to connect with like-minded  sustainability experts on the dancefloor.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"8a96b267-fa3f-4b2b-bbaa-accf67fdf440\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"size\": \"h3\", \"heading_text\": \"Symbiosis in Development (SiD) book launch\"}, \"id\": \"b42dae6f-a59d-4b38-ba15-9e9e53f25d98\", \"type\": \"heading_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>At our anniversary, after 10 years of work, the first complete book on  Symbiosis in Development (SiD) will be launched. It is the first A to Z  workmanual for systemic sustainable development, capturing experience of  over 700 projects worldwide. This first limited hardcover edition has  100 unique hand-made illustrations and diagrams.\\u00a0 See for details about  SiD: <a href=\\\"http://www.thinksid.org/\\\">www.thinksid.org.</a> </p>\"}, \"id\": \"d46b668b-f2e5-46af-89b3-ffb74cd5ed57\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"image\": 41, \"attribution\": \"\", \"caption\": \"\"}, \"id\": \"9a8012e1-dbc5-4574-8a56-314f7eddee90\", \"type\": \"image_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"size\": \"h3\", \"heading_text\": \"Workshops & Celebration 20th September 2019 @ Utrecht Community\"}, \"id\": \"3f63e06f-3125-475a-a7be-a3053270b610\", \"type\": \"heading_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p> The workshops have a limited number of spaces available, so sign up fast via <a href=\\\"https://forms.gle/MG3XQXLKZBhsiXeW7\\\">this link</a>.\\u00a0 </p>\"}, \"id\": \"5f1c8468-a9d4-43bc-81d2-62e2d156de9c\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p> <b>Free Workshops</b></p><p></p><p>14.30 - 17.00 Integrated Sustainability Light hosted by Except</p><p></p><p><i>What does the future look like in 20 years? In this fun  &amp; light session we use the basics of SiD to tackle this question.  Max 12 participants.</i></p><p></p><p>14.30 - 17.00 Draw your Future hosted by Eveline Mos</p><p></p><p><i>As we&#x27;re looking back and forward, how do you envision  your own future? Learn techniques for visually drawing your own future  in this workshop. Max 20 participant.</i></p><p></p><p>14.30 - 17.00 Community Garden: how to create &amp; enjoy your own?\\u00a0 hosted by Except\\u00a0 &amp; Suzanne van den Berk</p><p></p><p><i>We share our experiences, positive effects, teach about  specific veggies &amp; edible plants and do a tasting. Max 15  participants.\\u00a0</i></p>\"}, \"id\": \"3492c05e-029e-4ed6-8b91-e68024ffe9bd\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p><b>Evening Anniversary Celebration</b></p><p></p><p>17.00 - 17.30 Walk in\\u00a0</p><p></p><p>17.30 - 19.00 Inspiring stories looking back and into the future</p><p>                       Book launch: Symbiosis in Development (SiD)</p><p>                       Launch of the Except Sustainability Academy</p><p>                       Performance by the ALMA Quartet</p><p></p><p>19.00 - 21.00 Dinner by Instock\\u00a0</p><p></p><p>21.00 - 23.00 DJs and Dance\\u00a0</p>\"}, \"id\": \"a46db86c-5305-4248-a7bc-5affa5c8aee6\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"size\": \"h3\", \"heading_text\": \"Registration\"}, \"id\": \"ce2ea541-ec38-4881-963b-bbbc562f639a\", \"type\": \"heading_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p> Please register for parts of the program via <a href=\\\"https://forms.gle/MG3XQXLKZBhsiXeW7\\\"><b>this link</b></a>.<br/></p><p>For any questions, contact Saskia (saskia@except.nl). <br/>Follow our <a href=\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/except---integrated-sustainability/\\\">LinkedIn</a> and <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/home\\\">Twitter</a> for our highlighted projects and further announcements.\\u00a0 </p>\"}, \"id\": \"8646149d-b92a-45b0-a53f-1e1d125ef7df\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}]','[{\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We celebrate with the unique and amazing people that have traveled this  path with us together all those years. Expect a full day program, free  workshops, inspiring stories from partners, and a big party at the  end.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"b7d6c806-c653-4ba5-bab8-51effaf4ffd9\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"size\": \"h4\", \"heading_text\": \"Anniversary program\"}, \"id\": \"05f75a66-61ee-4824-b1a2-d03a158fd76a\", \"type\": \"heading_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>During the day, we offer sustainability pioneers multiple free  workshops. What would the world look like in 20 years? Use our SiD  framework to have fun while learning about integrated sustainability.  Eveline Mos will teach you how to envision your own future by using  visual dialogue techniques, and we will share our experiences with  setting up a community garden.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"c2909535-12fe-412a-8804-fb817a6646ad\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"text\": \"<p>We ask our partners to share their stories on their own past and future  journey, and launch the first complete SiD book \\u2013\\u00a0 followed by a dinner  provided by Instock. We end with a party to connect with like-minded  sustainability experts on the dancefloor.</p>\"}, \"id\": \"8a96b267-fa3f-4b2b-bbaa-accf67fdf440\", \"type\": \"paragraph_block\"}, {\"value\": {\"siz