INSERT INTO `people_peoplepage` VALUES (14,'except_team_top.jpg','Meet our team','Meet our team','People','Leading sustainability consultants & designers','Leading sustainability consultants & designers','Leading sustainability consultants & designers','Our Team','Our Team','Our Team','Except is an international collective of pioneers, talented and motivated sustainability experts in over 20 disciplines. We are immensely proud of our unique team: without our diversity, experience, and dedication, we could never work on such a variety of pioneering projects. Most of our experts speak multiple languages, and are available on an individual basis as well as in team form.','Except is an international collective of pioneers, talented and motivated sustainability experts in over 20 disciplines. We are immensely proud of our unique team: without our diversity, experience, and dedication, we could never work on such a variety of pioneering projects. Most of our experts speak multiple languages, and are available on an individual basis as well as in team form.','Except is a collective of pioneers, talented and motivated sustainability experts in over 20 disciplines, and from multiple different countries. We are immensely proud of our unique team: without our diversity, experience, and dedication, we could never work on such a variety of pioneering projects. Most of our experts speak multiple languages, and are available on an individual basis as well as in team form.','Our team includes environmental and social scientists, designers, facilitators, engineers, software developers, and business developers. We are practical and committed social entrepreneurs, and we stand by our clients in any challenge.','Our team includes environmental and social scientists, designers, facilitators, engineers, software developers, and business developers. We are practical and committed social entrepreneurs, and we stand by our clients in any challenge.','Our team includes social and environmental scientists, designers, facilitators, engineers, software developers, and business developers. We are practical and committed social entrepreneurs, and we love standing by our clients in any challenge.',1,1);
