INSERT INTO `services_servicepage` VALUES (17,'Flourishing Places','Flourishing Places','Flourishing Places','Creating resilient cities, building & regions','Creating resilient cities, building & regions','Creating resilient cities, building & regions','green','We realize beautiful places to love, work, and play. Cities and buildings ready to face the future;  healthy and safe, self-powered, regenerative, and inspiring to behold.\r\n\r\nSince 1999 we develop exemplary sustainable cities, buildings, regions, neighborhoods, resorts, and islands. We guide the process from soaring vision to practical realization with solid science, engineering, design, and process management.','We realize beautiful places to love, work, and play. Cities and buildings ready to face the future;  healthy and safe, self-powered, regenerative, and inspiring to behold.\r\n\r\nSince 1999 we develop exemplary sustainable cities, buildings, regions, neighborhoods, resorts, and islands. We guide the process from soaring vision to practical realization with solid science, engineering, design, and process management.','We realize beautiful places to love, work, and play. Cities and buildings ready to face the future;  healthy and safe, self-powered, regenerative, and inspiring to behold.\r\n\r\nSince 1999 we develop exemplary sustainable cities, buildings, regions, neighborhoods, resorts, and islands. We guide the process from soaring vision to practical realization with solid science, engineering, design, and process management.',75,'Creating resilient cities, building & regions'),(22,'Future-proof Organizations','Future-proof Organizations','Future-proof Organizations','Empowering companies, governments & communities','Empowering companies, governments & communities','Empowering companies, governments & communities','blue','The world is on the move towards sustainability, within companies, governments, and institutions alike. Where is your organization  in its transition towards its sustainable  