, \"pk\": 17, \"search_description_nl\": \"\", \"draft_title\": \"Sustainable Places, Cities & Buildings\", \"introduction_en\": \"We realize beautiful places to love, work, and play. Cities and buildings ready to face the future;  healthy and safe, self-powered, regenerative, and inspiring to behold.\\r\\n\\r\\nSince 1999 we develop exemplary sustainable cities, buildings, regions, neighborhoods, resorts, and islands. We guide the process from soaring vision to practical realization with solid science, engineering, design, and process management.\", \"hero_subtitle_nl\": null, \"url_path_en\": \"/except-integrated-sustainability/services/sustainable-places-cities-buildings/\", \"slug_en\": \"sustainable-places-cities-buildings\", \"seo_title_nl\": null}',NULL,17,1),(31,0,'2019-09-14 14:53:18.735207','{\"slug_nl\": null, \"numchild\": 0, \"seo_title\": \"\", \"hero_title_nl\": null, \"title_nl\": null, \"pk\": 18, \"first_published_at\": null, \"search_description_nl\": \"\", \"slug_en\": \"urban-renaissance\", \"has_unpublished_changes\": false, \"content_type\": 38, \"description_en\": \"The Urban Renaissance program delivers redevelopment plans for sustainable cities and neighborhoods, integrating all major sustainability aspects in one program. Its approach works across all social, economic, ecological and physical aspects of a city.  \\r\\n\\r\\nThe approach works for large metropolis,  regional centers and small towns. It delivers each, to their scale and capacity, the power of advanced strategic planning, circular economies, healthy and smart cities, renewable energy, and resilient bio-based economies.\", \"body\": \"[{\\\"value\\\": {\\\"image\\\": 16, \\\"attribution\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"caption\\\": \\\"\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"366396b5-f18f-48de-9463-e5496d75a240\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"image_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"size\\\": \\\"h3\\\", \\\"heading_text\\\": \\\"Why develop an integrated urban strategy plan?\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"de64316e-c5f7-43f7-86fa-592b1ac9763b\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"heading_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"text\\\": \\\"<p><b>With the Urban Renaissance program municipalities can boost their  resilience and sustainability quickly and efficiently. Cities can now  use the power of the knowledge gained in developing advanced urban  strategies in urban plans around the world, and implement them more  efficiently in an integrated program.</b> </p>\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"8cc07db7-4ba7-4c61-b31a-db5581e88f07\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"paragraph_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"image\\\": 17, \\\"attribution\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"caption\\\": \\\"\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"6979799d-550a-4a52-a777-8724815e76b8\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"image_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"image\\\": 18, \\\"attribution\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"caption\\\": \\\"\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"06ba0d66-517b-49f6-8a63-702855f0a03b\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"image_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"size\\\": \\\"h3\\\", \\\"heading_text\\\": \\\"Integrate best practices across all urban areas\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"cdab3299-2520-48a6-8423-e8dde2dab47f\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"heading_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"text\\\": \\\"<p> The Urban Renaissance program integrates the best urban renewal practices in  one holistic urban redevelopment approach. With this, we deliver  circular smart and resilient city strategy plans in a relatively short  time frame, from one year for small to mid-sized cities to two years for  larger ones. </p>\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"7f60793e-9964-437f-9138-dc2ac24d63fe\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"paragraph_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"image\\\": 19, \\\"attribution\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"caption\\\": \\\"\\\"}, \\\"id\\\": \\\"dd957920-4dd5-429c-8eda-9491e56eef58\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"image_block\\\"}, {\\\"value\\\": {\\\"text\\\": \\\"<p>These boost the use of renewable energy sources, provide clean air and  water, generate longer lasting jobs, and make for livable, healthy, and  beautiful cities with a stable economy. Integrated ur