Monday, we have a shared lunch, every other Monday we all meet up, and teams work together on a daily basis in our main office in Utrecht.</li><li>We give space for self expression and development, to learn new skills, and grow within the\\\\u00a0 organization, and expect you to give a cutting edge performance in return.</li><li>We operate within a flat hierarchy. You can initiate and contribute to any project, and have the responsibility to follow through.\\\\u00a0 If you need\\\\u00a0 a lot of guidance, or support in organizing yourself, we may not be for you.</li><li>We travel internationally, a lot. Have your passport ready.</li><li>We speak English at the office.</li><li>We maintain a 4 day work week.</li><li>We provide only public transportation and bicycle allowances for commuting.</li></ul>\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"paragraph_block\\\"}, {\\\"id\\\": \\\"0379facf-1dd6-4109-b55b-5a4b3f841c39\\\", \\\"value\\\": {\\\"heading_text\\\": \\\"Interns and trainees\\\", \\\"size\\\": \\\"h4\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"heading_block\\\"}, {\\\"id\\\": \\\"7fcde1ed-1a31-4425-be38-d031633be11e\\\", \\\"value\\\": {\\\"text\\\": \\\"<p>We are open for a limited number of internships and trainee positions each year. These are not your easy run-of-the-mill internships, and are at minimum 6 months. You&#x27;ll be pushed to your limits and receive a lot of freedom and responsibility. We want you to stay if it works well, which is the goal of the traineeship program. If that&#x27;s what you want, read on. For trainees, answer the seperate set of questions at the end in your application.</p>\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"paragraph_block\\\"}, {\\\"id\\\": \\\"b8adddc5-0f20-41d0-bea2-ea0de78c9794\\\", \\\"value\\\": {\\\"attribution\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"image\\\": 8, \\\"caption\\\": \\\"\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"image_block\\\"}, {\\\"id\\\": \\\"7a554906-be06-4422-ab82-3661c75cd5c5\\\", \\\"value\\\": {\\\"heading_text\\\": \\\"Our work ethic\\\", \\\"size\\\": \\\"h3\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \